{"tid":346461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解雙子座可以咁仆街","createTime":"2017-08-04T03:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T07:04:47.000Z","uid":51382,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19deb46bcec4aa1e6fa7e364e258e5324acaf881","tid":346461,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"我就係呢個仆街 點解成日做野都三分鐘熱度 <br />\n半途而廢 郁啲就放棄 <br />\n次次都得把口 講完又做唔到 份人又輕挑浮誇 <br />\n成熟小小都唔得 永遠成個小朋友<br />\n 係啊 初初你係吸引到人地注意啊 但有撚用咩  <br />\n成日擺副玩世不恭嘅樣 人地走左 你開心啦 你自由啦 <br />\n我真係想改 但我唔知點解次次最後都搞成咁 <br />\n點解你唔可以比多次機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b79ad8ba726ee72e5631b11dc1c52ab65947c48","tid":346461,"uid":50483,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"關星座撚事咩"},{"pid":"57a513a053bcec9cacc027df5fbfd26f0591a121","tid":346461,"uid":24559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"咪係 個人仆街都要賴落星座度"},{"pid":"ff0c9237aab415de512931d7dafe93c67bf74edf","tid":346461,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"啱啦 屌醒我嗨"},{"pid":"901d232ea88948f5768fcea1199c978a9a6cde73","tid":346461,"uid":51382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"改一改標題 點解我可以咁仆街"},{"pid":"13a4ec13f45aaa3d45cff958ab58e3ba2e191843","tid":346461,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46542299c003c804336ee32ee01c791b647165f8","tid":346461,"uid":82398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"On9 你𡃤得星座就知你份人幾廢幾無料幾on99"},{"pid":"390e3eb6f72d057de2ba2016e6cc706720f7511b","tid":346461,"uid":4526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"21世紀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{